{"tid":1560781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【毋忘初心】諗返最初點解要出嚟","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:48:53.000Z","uid":108360,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a7d8e54e7b458a34da9000ce82d65100229dfe","tid":1560781,"uid":108360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IMy4SNe3O1Y?t=148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIMy4SNe3O1Y%3Ft%3D148&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=43946197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IMy4SNe3O1Y?t=148</a> 2:28開始聽<br />\n由6月到依家，發生好多事，好似大家都失咗焦，五毛亦開始散佈無力感<br />\n我想用呢段MV令大家諗返起最初果種心情，點解會主動出嚟行，唔好俾自己麻木<br />\n<br />\n如果香港拎唔返自由同自治，結果會點，相信大家都好清楚<br />\n依家<span style=\"color: blue;\">放棄</span>，莫講話義士，你<span style=\"color: red;\">對唔對得住之前出過嚟嘅自己，對唔對得住未來要經歷Chinazi嘅自己</span><br />\n<br />\nquote 攬炒巴嘅一段字：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">與其以絕望迎接2047終局，倒不如趁香港尚有一絲餘暉之時奮力一搏，善用僅存的國際價值，與中共「攬炒」。此乃第二重先破後立之意&mdash;&mdash; 置諸死地而後生。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"daa3dffa8c4aa621c8a5920807f46427b7953763","tid":1560781,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"p